The '''Brookshire Katy Drainage District''' ('''BKDD''') is a political subdivision of the state of [[Texas]] which oversees the drainage of water within its boundaries.<ref>"[http://www.bkddonline.com/about.html About the BKDD]." Brookshire Katy Drainage District. Retrieved on July 17, 2010.</ref> The district has its headquarters in [[Brookshire, Texas|Brookshire]], [[Texas]].<ref>"[http://www.bkddonline.com/contact.php Contact BKDD]." Brookshire Katy Drainage District. Retrieved on July 17, 2010.</ref>

